Grammar

    0 $accept: program $end

    1 program: decList

    2 decList: decList declaration
    3        | declaration

    4 declaration: typeDecl
    5            | funDecl
    6            | varDecl
    7            | statement

    8 typeDecl: TYPE IDENTIFIER LEFT_BRACE varDeclList RIGHT_BRACE

    9 funDecl: FUN IDENTIFIER function

   10 function: LEFT_PAREN parameters RIGHT_PAREN ARROW var_type block
   11         | LEFT_PAREN RIGHT_PAREN ARROW var_type block

   12 parameters: parameters COMMA typedVar
   13           | typedVar

   14 typedVar: IDENTIFIER COLON var_type

   15 var_type: INT
   16         | FLOAT
   17         | STRING
   18         | BOOL
   19         | DYN
   20         | LIST LEFT_SQUARE INT_CONSTANT RIGHT_SQUARE
   21         | IDENTIFIER

   22 varDeclList: varDeclList varDecl
   23            | varDecl

   24 varDecl: VAR var_type IDENTIFIER EQ expression SEMI_COLON
   25        | VAR var_type IDENTIFIER SEMI_COLON

   26 statement: exprStmt
   27          | forStmt
   28          | ifStmt
   29          | echoStmt
   30          | returnStmt
   31          | whileStmt
   32          | dowhileStmt
   33          | breakStmt
   34          | continueStmt
   35          | block

   36 exprStmt: expression SEMI_COLON

   37 forStmt: FOR LEFT_PAREN forInit optExpr SEMI_COLON optExpr RIGHT_PAREN statement

   38 forInit: varDecl
   39        | exprStmt
   40        | SEMI_COLON

   41 optExpr: expression
   42        | ε

   43 ifStmt: IF LEFT_PAREN expression RIGHT_PAREN statement ELSE statement
   44       | IF LEFT_PAREN expression RIGHT_PAREN statement

   45 echoStmt: ECH expression SEMI_COLON

   46 returnStmt: RET expression SEMI_COLON
   47           | RET SEMI_COLON

   48 whileStmt: WHILE LEFT_PAREN expression RIGHT_PAREN statement

   49 dowhileStmt: DO statement WHILE LEFT_PAREN expression RIGHT_PAREN SEMI_COLON

   50 breakStmt: BREAK SEMI_COLON

   51 continueStmt: CONTINUE SEMI_COLON

   52 block: LEFT_BRACE decList RIGHT_BRACE
   53      | LEFT_BRACE RIGHT_BRACE

   54 expression: assignment

   55 assignment: call_access EQ assignment
   56           | call_access PLUS_EQ assignment
   57           | call_access MINUS_EQ assignment
   58           | call_access STAR_EQ assignment
   59           | call_access SLASH_EQ assignment
   60           | call_access PERC_EQ assignment
   61           | ternary

   62 ternary: logic_or QUESTION_MARK ternary COLON ternary
   63        | logic_or

   64 logic_or: logic_or DOUBLE_PIPE logic_and
   65         | logic_and

   66 logic_and: logic_and DOUBLE_AND bitwise_or
   67          | bitwise_or

   68 bitwise_or: bitwise_or PIPE bitwise_xor
   69           | bitwise_xor

   70 bitwise_xor: bitwise_xor XOR bitwise_and
   71            | bitwise_and

   72 bitwise_and: bitwise_and AND equality
   73            | equality

   74 equality: equality BANG_EQ comparison
   75         | equality EQ_EQ comparison
   76         | comparison

   77 comparison: comparison GREATER shift
   78           | comparison LESS shift
   79           | comparison GREATER_EQ shift
   80           | comparison LESS_EQ shift
   81           | shift

   82 shift: shift SHIFT_LEFT term
   83      | shift SHIFT_RIGHT term
   84      | term

   85 term: term PLUS factor
   86     | term MINUS factor
   87     | factor

   88 factor: factor SLASH unary
   89       | factor STAR unary
   90       | factor PERC unary
   91       | unary

   92 unary: BANG unary
   93      | TILDE unary
   94      | MINUS unary
   95      | PLUS_PLUS unary
   96      | MINUS_MINUS unary
   97      | call_access

   98 call_access: call_access LEFT_PAREN arguments RIGHT_PAREN
   99            | call_access LEFT_PAREN RIGHT_PAREN
  100            | call_access DOT IDENTIFIER
  101            | call_access LEFT_SQUARE expression RIGHT_SQUARE
  102            | call_access PLUS_PLUS
  103            | call_access MINUS_MINUS
